name: Rocket Crash
description:
Ready to control the uncontrollable? This rocket has a few malfunctions that will make hard to pilot, and that will often lead it to go out of control! Can you beat the 3 levels by getting the rocket to the end platform each time?

Use UP, DOWN, LEFT, RIGHT arrows to move around.

Assets used:

Skybox: Farland Skies from Borodar

Rocket Sprite: Here
